## Basic settings

set previewer ~/.config/lf/previewer

# set hidden on
set drawbox on
set icons on

## Favorites

map `a cd /mnt/user/Anime/Current
map `` cd ~

## Hotkeys

# Start current shell (ranger behavior)
map S $$SHELL
map f :filter
map <enter> open
map D delete
map <esc> reset
map <f-2> rename

## Basic commands

# mkdir that create single dir, no quote required for spaces (ranger behavior)
cmd mkdir %IFS=" "; mkdir -- "$*"

# all-in-one reset
cmd reset :{{
    :clear
    :unselect
    :setfilter
}}